<span class="displaytext">the (candidate full) presidential committee today announced the launch of a new radio ad entitled "comisionada sosa y alcalde robaina." the ad is airing on spanish language radio in florida and features hialeah mayor julio robaina and miami-dade county commissioner rebeca sosa. <p>to listen to the ad, click here: <a href="http://www.blip.tv/file/600422">http://www.blip.tv/file/600422</a>. the script is below. </p><p><u><strong>script for "comisionada sosa y alcalde robaina":</strong></u> </p><p><strong>mayor julio robaina:</strong> "les habla su alcalde julio robaina la experiencia no se improvisa. la persona con la experiencia necesaria para ser un gran presidente es (candidate full). (candidate last) tiene la experiencia para proteger a nuestras familias. él tiene la experiencia para manejar los momentos difíciles que confronta todo presidente." </p><p><strong>commissioner rebeca sosa:</strong> "les habla su comisionada rebecca sosa.me preguntan que busco en el próximo presidente de los estados unidos – que tenga liderazgo probado. esa es la razón por la que apoyo a (candidate full). recordemos el dolor de aquel 11 de septiembre cuando esta gran nación enfrento unos de los momentos más difíciles de su historia. en ese momento, (candidate full) creció y demostró sus cualidades de compasión y liderazgo votemos por el líder probado. votemos por (candidate full)." </p><p><strong>narrator:</strong> "(candidate full) – presidente" </p><p><strong>mayor (candidate last):</strong> "soy (candidate full) y apruebo este mensaje." </p><p><strong>narrator:</strong> "pagado por the (candidate full) presidential committee incorporated." </p><p><u><strong>english translation:</strong></u> </p><p><strong>mayor julio robaina:</strong> "this is your mayor julio robaina. you can't improvise (make up) experience. the person with the necessary experience to be a great president is (candidate full)." </p><p><strong>mayor julio robaina:</strong> "(candidate last) has the experience to protect our families. he has the experience to handle those difficult moments that all presidents face." </p><p><strong>commissioner rebeca sosa:</strong> "this is your commissioner rebecca sosa. i'm asked what i'm looking for in the next president of the united states – that they have proven leadership. that is the reason why i support (candidate full). let's remember the pain of that september 11th, when this great country faced one of the most difficult times of its history. at that moment, (candidate full) rose to the occasion and showed us his qualities of compassion and leadership. let's vote for the proven leader. let's vote for (candidate full)." </p><p><strong>narrator:</strong> "(candidate full)- president" </p><p><strong>mayor (candidate last):</strong> "i'm (candidate full) and i approve this message." </p><p><strong>narrator:</strong> "paid for by the (candidate full) presidential committee incorporated."</p></span>



